Tu-160 Blackjack Revision I (future updates)

3225 units of fuel for four turbofan engines. It has a ridiculous range, and it's extremely agile and stable for TERCOM bombing runs.

3 full length bomb bays and heavy duty landing gear.

Press 1 to toggle bomb bays.

Download: [https://www.dropbox.com/s/gkgjk5m0hz0ncqy/Tu-160-2.craft?dl=0](https://www.dropbox.com/s/gkgjk5m0hz0ncqy/Tu-160-2.craft?dl=0)
